Locally owned, f

POP QUIZ:  THIS 7-11 is a: a. great place to get a flat soda.
b. get hit up for change.
c. almost get robbed.
d. all of the above.
correct answer: d

On more than one occasion I have had to point out that something I was purchasing was on sale.
I have also picked up Mountain Dew that was a month expired and yesterday a Fat Tire beer that was expired.
If it wasn't a two minute walk from my apartment I would avoid it.

